::Windlord::

Windlord looked at Areotaur and later at the pod.

"Maybe... I can do that the bot left stasis lock... This bot just 
need some energy to leave stasis lock"

Windlord quit off some plants of pod's control and he used a link and 
connected it to the pod

"Download weapons' energy... "

The process started but for Windlord's the pain was high. He tried to 
hold his moans but dificultly he could. At least the process ended 
and a discharge of energy trow away at Windlord as if a thunder had 
hit him and discharge stun him.

Pod's computer say "Retiring stasis lock... proces will end in 6 
minutes".
